OL,3,CNew Forest wildfire destroys heathland
OL,4,Cnear Beaulieu
OL,6,FFirefighters have been tackling a
OL,7,Fwildfire in the New Forest which
OL,8,Fdestroyed 15 hectares of heath and
OL,9,Fgorse.
OL,11,FThe alarm was raised at around 5pm on
OL,12,FSaturday, 18 April, after flames were
OL,13,Fspotted at Bagshot Moor in East Boldre
OL,14,Fnear Beaulieu.
OL,16,FAround 40 firefighters from nine
OL,17,Fstations worked to bring the fire
OL,18,Funder control.
OL,20,FThe stop came in shortly after 7.30pm
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
